Blanket approval for other than the moneymover group is essential for the NCD. These documents are used for extremely time sensitive payments, e.g. IRS deposits and benefit payments. It is essential that the initiator be able to blanket approve so documents aren't hung up in routing. The moneymove group alwasy serves as a second "approver" for NCD generated payments. This WorkGroup is to extend the group of MONEYMOVER to include ADMINISTRATORS for the sake of blanket approving NonCheckDisbursementDocument instances
